00:00:06.566 --> 00:00:09.019
today we will make almond cookies.

00:00:09.196 --> 00:00:13.776
these are specially prepared during the festive season of christmas.

00:00:14.170 --> 00:00:19.908
let's see what all ingredients are required for making alomds cookies.

00:00:20.804 --> 00:00:22.471
maida - 1 cup

00:00:23.139 --> 00:00:24.949
powdered sugar- 1/2 cup

00:00:25.476 --> 00:00:27.134
ghee - 1/2 cup

00:00:27.493 --> 00:00:34.249
almonds - 1/2 cup (keep 10-12 almonds and make powder from rest)

00:00:34.851 --> 00:00:37.232
baking powder - .45 tsp

00:00:37.719 --> 00:00:44.728
for making almond cookies mix sugar and ghee completely.

00:00:59.313 --> 00:01:08.174
whisk the mixture nicely for 3-4 minuts until it appears smooth and white in color.

00:01:19.816 --> 00:01:25.740
mix bakiong powder and almond powder in maida.

00:01:33.757 --> 00:01:43.318
mic it thoroughly by straining the mixture with sieve or like this by using spoon.

00:01:44.872 --> 00:01:49.594
now add this mixture in ghee-sugar batter.

00:01:53.157 --> 00:01:58.680
stir until all ingredients blend nicely.

00:02:00.067 --> 00:02:08.866
add almond powder as well and mix all ingredients thoroughly.

00:02:09.174 --> 00:02:14.150
if the batter is dry then add 1-2 tbsp milk into it.

00:02:21.264 --> 00:02:25.820
add 1 tbsp milk as dough is dry.

00:02:35.156 --> 00:02:37.998
dough for making cookies is ready.

00:02:41.123 --> 00:02:43.917
grease tray with some oil.

00:02:50.488 --> 00:02:56.183
dice one almond into two halfs.

00:02:59.101 --> 00:03:02.130
take little amount of dough and roll it.

00:03:05.006 --> 00:03:11.668
flatten it and place one half of the almond.

00:03:14.628 --> 00:03:18.977
place cookies at some distance as they will puff up.

00:03:22.292 --> 00:03:27.947
now place the cookies for baking in preheated oven.

00:03:41.363 --> 00:03:46.795
bake cookies for 15-16 minutes on 180 degree centigrade.

00:03:51.363 --> 00:03:58.627
cookies have become light brown in color so take them out in a separate plate.

00:03:59.038 --> 00:04:04.284
cookies are ready and with this much quantity we have prepared 18 cookies.

